<< Does anyone have any idea how to "open" up a fuel gauge (12 volt)?  >>

Hi Guido,
If it is a stock bus one that has the bezel curve with the dash, do not open 
it!  We have tried over and over and they all crack when removing the bezel.  
Best to send it to a VDO repair shop and see if they can fix it or not 
instead.   Eric&Barb
